line of code---logics--- flow control
issues ---- error and exception

flow control ---- some distrubtion(any reason) have affected to stop the interpeter flow know as issues and its
show in log file.

error  ---- human issues :- not follow the language rules and regulation (Syntax Error)

exception :- some unwanted event(logical issues) that distrube the flow, know as exception.
its know as run time error.

in python everything is an object, and python is working in interpeter, when exception is arise
that time, its break the flow and raise issue in console bar. and its stop the execution.

